title: NFL Coaching Cycle Winners & Losers with Jonathan Jones (Football 1/14)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jonathan Jones to assess the winners (4:15) & losers (32:45) of the 2020 NFL coaching cycle, evaluating hirings, firings, and non-moves that will make big impacts on next season and beyond.
